  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Procurement audit in the research support to Rwanda and Etiopien</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Upphandlingsrevision inom forskningsst&#xF6;det till Rwanda och Etiopien</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Procurement audit in research support to Rwanda and Ethiopia. This decision replaces decision 2017-000587, as a higher maximum amount is required to receive tenders.

Coordinators for several of the bilateral research grants have expressed dissatisfaction with the way the procurements are conducted at their university. We need to get a better idea of ??how big the problems are. Therefore, it is proposed that a procurement audit be carried out at two of the universities that receive research support from Sida, the University of Rwanda and the University of Addis Ababa in Ethiopia. The first is a relatively new support and the latter has been going on for a long time. In both cases, you follow the national procurement rules that are deemed to be met according to Sida.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Upphandlingsrevision inom forskningsst&#xF6;det till Rwanda och Etiopien. Detta beslut ers&#xE4;tter beslut 2017-000587, d&#xE5; ett h&#xF6;gre maxbelopp kr&#xE4;vs f&#xF6;r att f&#xE5; in anbud.

Koordinat&#xF6;rer f&#xF6;r flera av de bilaterala forskningsst&#xF6;den har uttryckt otillfredsst&#xE4;llelse ang&#xE5;ende hur upphandlingarna sk&#xF6;ts p&#xE5; deras universitet. Vi beh&#xF6;ver f&#xE5; en b&#xE4;ttre bild av hur stora problemen &#xE4;r. D&#xE4;rf&#xF6;r f&#xF6;resl&#xE5;s att en upphandlingsrevision genomf&#xF6;rs p&#xE5; tv&#xE5; av universiteten som f&#xE5;r forskningsst&#xF6;d fr&#xE5;n Sida, University of Rwanda och Universityof Addis Abeba i Etiopien. Det f&#xF6;rsta &#xE4;r ett relativ nytt st&#xF6;d och den senare har p&#xE5;g&#xE5;tt under l&#xE5;ng tid. I b&#xE5;da fallen f&#xF6;ljer man de nationella upphandlingsreglerna som bed&#xF6;mts vara tillfylles enligt Sida.</narrative>
  </description>
